hi! this is a readme file for the backend of the motorsport voting fullstack app.
Since it is my first time building a fullstack app,
I will most likely have mistakes in the code. Future more complex versions will show improvements.

this is a monorepo project, the backend is build with fastapi whereas I used claude to build the
the frontend using talwind css and react. This app is a voting app for motorsport fans, 
simply said, its to represent real time backend to frontend communication.
